d":5088,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/14\/pride-arrogance-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":24789,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Allah will throw proud, arrogant into Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Grandeur is My cloak and pride is My garment. Whoever competes with Me in one of these two, I will cast him into the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4090 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14871,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/arrogance-exalt-himself-tyrant\/","url_meta":{"origin":24789,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Man exalts himself until he becomes a tyrant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salamah ibn al-Akwa' reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man continues to exalt himself until he is recorded among the tyrants. He will be punished as they are punished.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2000 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0639\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"clas